abstract: Real Madrid tops Spanish standings with win over Athletic Bilbao and Celta Vigo reaches second place with win over Barcelona; other soccer news noted.
lead_paragraph: Celta Vigo swept to a shocking 4-1 victory over visiting Barcelona, and Real Madrid went to the top of the Spanish standings with a 2-1 win at Athletic Bilbao.

headline.main: Barcelona Loses; Real Madrid Moves Into First
headline.print_headline: Barcelona Loses; Real Madrid Moves Into First
